### Top Issues and Drivers
| Issue | Calls | % | Driver | Dimension | Solution |
|---|---|---|---|---|---|
| Customer's cashback was posted as points instead of statement credit. They can't find where to change their redemption preference. | 7 | 43.75% | primary | digital | Enhance the findability of redemption preference settings within the rewards dashboard. Provide clear options for customers to select and manage their preferred cashback method. |
| Customer used their card at a gas station but didn't get the 5x gas category bonus. The merchant coded as 'convenience store'. | 3 | 18.75% | secondary | digital | Improve transparency around merchant category coding and its impact on bonus eligibility by displaying MCC and applied earn rate for each transaction, with an explainer for MCC map... |
| Customer signed up for a 60,000 point welcome bonus offer but only received 40,000 after meeting the spend requirement. | 2 | 12.5% | secondary | digital | Provide clear, real-time tracking of welcome bonus progress and transparent communication of all qualifying criteria, including an in-app offer tracker with a progress bar and a se... |
| Customer was downgraded from Platinum to Gold tier without any warning or notification. Lost access to airport lounge benefit. | 1 | 6.25% | secondary | digital | Implement proactive communication and visibility for tier status changes and qualification progress, including a tier progress dashboard and 60-day advance warnings for downgrades. |
| Customer's anniversary bonus points from last year haven't been credited. Account anniversary was 3 months ago. | 1 | 6.25% | secondary | digital | Provide digital visibility into the status and expected posting of anniversary bonus points, including a dedicated section in the rewards dashboard and push notifications. |
| Customer made $300 in grocery purchases last month but points for the 3x category bonus weren't credited. Regular 1x points were applied. | 1 | 6.25% | secondary | digital | Improve transparency around category bonus eligibility and any associated caps or exclusions by displaying applied earn rates and category bonus details within transaction details. |
| Customer transferred points to airline partner 5 days ago but they still don't appear in the airline frequent flyer account. | 1 | 6.25% | secondary | digital | Implement a digital tracking mechanism for points transfers to external partners, including estimated completion times, status updates, and clear irreversibility warnings. |

### Quick Wins
- Enhance the findability of redemption preference settings within the rewards dashboard. Provide clear options for customers to select and manage their preferred cashback method.
- Improve transparency around merchant category coding and its impact on bonus eligibility. Educate customers on how transactions are categorized.
- Provide clear, real-time tracking of welcome bonus progress and transparent communication of all qualifying criteria.
- Implement proactive communication and visibility for tier status changes and qualification progress.
- Provide digital visibility into the status and expected posting of anniversary bonus points.
- Improve transparency around category bonus eligibility and any associated caps or exclusions.

